      <title>指引缓解美国担忧后，Entain 股价创 10 月以来最大涨幅</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/entain-gains-most-since-october-after-guidance-eases-us-concerns</link>
      <description><![CDATA[博彩公司 Entain Plc（Ladbrokes 母公司）股价在改善了有关 2024 年业绩预期的宣传后，创下自 10 月份以来的最大涨幅，缓解了人们对第四季度美国客户友好型业绩将侵蚀其利润的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/entain-gains-most-since-october-after-guidance-eases-us-concerns</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 09:04:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
