    <item>
      <title>印度资产遭受重创，卢比跌破 86 创下新低</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/rupee-falls-past-86-to-new-record-on-dollar-rally-oil-surge</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美元走强和油价上涨，人们更加担心印度这个全球增长最快的主要经济体之一将陷入经济放缓，印度资产遭到抛售，导致卢比出现近两年来最大跌幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/rupee-falls-past-86-to-new-record-on-dollar-rally-oil-surge</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 04:57:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由于美国对俄罗斯的制裁威胁供应，油价创下五个月新高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-12/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-jan-13</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美国对俄罗斯能源行业实施新一轮制裁，威胁到全球最大产油国之一的石油供应，油价上涨至五个月来的最高水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-12/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-jan-13</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 12 Jan 2025 23:02:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
